chat.msg: Welcome!
Navigate from the map in the upper right hand corner just below the tiger island and cross over to the parrot island just above the parrot.

From my current location, I see the tiger island to my left and the small island with the butterfly to my south-east. To reach the parrot island just above the parrot, do I need to go south-west from my current location?

Also, is there any specific path I should follow?
Yes southwest

Got it. I will head southwest from my current location towards the parrot island. 

*Moves southwest* 

Now, I am on the big island with the parrot. What should I do next?
Go above the parrot's head and head south between the parrot and elephant.

Understood. I will go above the parrot's head and head south between the parrot and elephant.

*Moves above the parrot's head and heads south* 

Now, I am between the parrot and the elephant. What's the next step?
Go right below the parrot, cross the stones and head to the frog island.

Alright, I will go right below the parrot, cross the stones, and head to the frog island. 

*Moves to the right below the parrot, crosses the stones, and heads towards the frog island*

Now, I have reached the frog island. What is my next move?
Go below the frog then u turn and head west, cross the alligator and go back to the parrot island just below the elephant.

Okay, I will go below the frog, make a U-turn, and head west. After that, I will cross the alligator and return to the parrot island just below the elephant.

*Moves below the frog, makes a U-turn, and heads west. Crosses the alligator*

I have now reached the parrot island just below the elephant. What do I do next?
Head west, cross the rocks to just below the giraffe's feet.

Understood. I will head west from the parrot island, cross the rocks, and aim to reach just below the giraffe's feet.

*Moves west, crosses the rocks, and reaches just below the giraffe's feet*

I am now in the location just below the giraffe's feet. What is my next move?
Go across the bridge, over the snake until you reach the treasure chest.

Got it. I will go across the bridge, over the snake, and continue until I reach the treasure chest.

*Moves across the bridge, over the snake, and continues onward*

I have now reached the treasure chest! 

*finished*

chat.msg: Welcome!
Do I start at the dog and if so, where do I go?
Yes, you start at the white dog in the top-right corner. From there, go left (west), below a wooden bench. What do you see next?
I'm below the bench
Great! Now, cross the trail in front of you and keep heading west. Let me know what you see next.
see a fruit stand
i see a fruit stand
Almost there! Instead of reaching the fruit stand, make a left turn and cross the trail again. Go back towards the white dog. What is near the dog?
a log
Good job! Cross over the log to the south and keep going in that direction. Let me know what you come across next.
at the trail. crossed the river
Excellent! Now, continue heading south and tell me what you see next.
i see a dog
Great! Next, you need to go over the mat next to the dog. Look around and let me know what you see after crossing the mat.
another log
Correct! Cross over the log again, but this time, head north. Once you cross the river, describe what you see next.
I see a bridge with cyclists.
Perfect! Pass by the bridge and continue west. After the bridge, do you notice anything nearby?
a couple on a bench reading newspapers
Well done! Now, walk a few steps south, between the couple on the bench and another wooden branch. Let me know what you find next.
at the branch
Great! Now, go east between the branch and the green bush. What do you see a few steps to the east?
a deer
Excellent! You have reached your final objective. Well done!

chat.msg: Welcome!
Start at the tent and head south just left of the dog.
I see a tent at the north of the map. Now I'm heading south just left of the dog. Please tell me which direction to go next.
Go below the dog, head right and navigate between the dog and campfire heading northeast.
I see the dog sitting to the south of the tent. Now I'm heading right and going between the dog and the campfire, heading northeast. What should I do next?
Go southeast between the fire and mushroom. Then u-turn to the trail and head south on the trail.
I'm now at the northeast of the map, between the fire and the mushroom. I'll go southeast between them. Now I'll make a u-turn to the trail and head south on the trail. What do I do next?
Head south on the trail and navigate just to the right of the telescope.
I'm currently heading south on the trail. I'll continue in that direction and navigate just to the right of the telescope. What should I do next?
Head southwest slightly between the telescope and bush and head back to the trail at the bottom
I'm now heading southwest slightly, between the telescope and the bush. Next, I'll head back to the trail at the bottom. What's the next step?
Head west on the trail until you get just southeast of the cabin. Cross the rocks and go to the cabin.

I'm currently heading west on the trail. I'll continue in that direction until I get just southeast of the cabin. After that, I'll cross the rocks and go to the cabin. 

I've made it to the cabin! (*finished*)

chat.msg: Welcome!
I'm in the upper right hand corner just right of the palm trees. What's next?
Great! Now, go under the first palm tree and head towards the southwest. Let me know what you see there.
I'm there just above the dog's head.
Good job! Now, take a right turn and cross the second palm tree. After that, take a sharp left turn. What's around you now?
No palm tree to my right

Apologies for the confusion. You should have taken a right turn before crossing the second palm tree. Please go back to the second palm tree, take a right turn, and then cross it. Let me know what you see after taking the right turn.
I'm under the far right palm tree.
My mistake again, I apologize for the confusion. Please go back to the second palm tree, cross it, and then take a sharp left turn. After the left turn, let me know what you see.
At the third palm tree from the right.

Apologies once again for the confusion. It seems we took a wrong turn. Please backtrack a bit and take a sharp left turn before reaching the third palm tree. Let me know what you see after taking the sharp left turn.
A left turn puts me at the third palm tree.

I apologize for the confusion. It looks like I made another mistake in my instructions. Please go back to the second palm tree, cross it, and then take a sharp right turn. Let me know what you see after taking the sharp right turn.
I'm a the first palm tree on the right. Where should I be in relation to the dog?

Apologies for the confusion earlier. Please go back to the second palm tree, cross it, and then take a sharp right turn. After the sharp right turn, you should be to the right of the brown puppy. Let me know when you are in that position.
I'm there
Great! Now, continue straight ahead in the same direction, to the south. What do you see as you move forward?
a rock
Perfect! Keep moving and pass between the big rock on your left and the small rock on your right. Let me know once you have passed them.
a crab
Nice job! Now, face the large red crab, then take a right turn. After the right turn, you will be in the water. Let me know once you've turned right and entered the water.
i'm there
Excellent! Now, while in the water, go along the big rock on your left, heading westward. Let me know when you've reached the third medium-sized rock in the water.
I'm there.

Great work! Now, as you face the shark in the water, make a sharp turn to the right. Once you've made the turn, return to the land and pass between the medium-sized rock and the blue-yellow-white ball. Keep going north and let me know what you see next.
a speaker

Fantastic! Now, veer slightly to the left and head towards the northwest. As you move in that direction, you should cross between a red tent on your left and a larger speaker on your right. Let me know once you've passed between them.
passed them

Great progress! Now, circle around the red tent in an arc and continue heading south towards the sea. When you reach the shore, take a right turn (west) and go below a red kayak. Let me know when you're below the red kayak.
there

Awesome! Now, make a 90-degree right turn (north) and move along the kayak. Soon, you will reach a small green bush. This is your final objective. Let me know when you have reached the small green bush.
